                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17881022-42-victim379 t17881022-42-viclabel192"></join>; my servant went out to gather her pots; and I heard a noise in the street; I thought it was her voice; and she said, here is a man has stole my pots; I laid hold of the prisoner, and sent for an officer, who came and searched him, and found a pint pot in his pocket, which was mine.</p>
               <p>
            
